tz.com/us-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/aipac-names-elliot-brandt-as-next-ceo-replacing-longtime-chief-howard-kohr/0000018f-e537-dce5-abdf-e73fec820000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院在拜登反对下通过国际刑事法院制裁法案，亲以色列民主党加入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-icc-sanctions-bill-amid-biden-opposition-with-pro-israel-dems-joining/0000018f-e4f9-db2a-a5ff-e4fbf3720000</link><description>该法案是对国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗向总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令的回应</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-icc-sanctions-bill-amid-biden-opposition-with-pro-israel-dems-joining/0000018f-e4f9-db2a-a5ff-e4fbf3720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队希望加剧黎巴嫩战斗，担心公众不知道后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-wants-to-intensify-lebanon-fighting-fears-public-unaware-of-consequences/0000018f-e4d0-d1da-adaf-f5dfa6ff0000</link><description>以色列国防军负责人表示，以色列已准备好向黎巴嫩发动攻势，旨在让公众为更广泛的冲突做好准备。战时内阁周二晚上召开会议，与真主党讨论升级问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-wants-to-intensify-lebanon-fighting-fears-public-unaware-of-consequences/0000018f-e4d0-d1da-adaf-f5dfa6ff0000</guid></item><item><title>斯洛文尼亚在政府支持的议会投票后承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-04/ty-article/slovenia-recognizes-palestinian-state-after-parliamentary-vote-with-government-support/0000018f-e4de-d11f-a5cf-e7df5fce0000</link><description>上周，斯洛文尼亚政府批准了一项承认巴勒斯坦国的动议，并将其提交议会最终批准。总理加快了这一进程，以回应以色列最近对拉法的袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:16:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-04/ty-article/slovenia-recognizes-palestinian-state-after-parliamentary-vote-with-government-support/0000018f-e4de-d11f-a5cf-e7df5fce0000</guid></item>