-hezbollah-says-it-does-not-want-to-expand-conflict/0000018f-e417-d1da-adaf-f59f16220001</link><description>卡塔尔表示已向哈马斯提交了以色列的停战建议 ■ 美国希望联合国安理会通过决议，支持拜登提出的停火协议 ■ 拜登告诉《时代》杂志，“有充分的理由”相信内塔尼亚胡出于政治考虑而延长战争■ 经过 20 小时与以色列北部的大火搏斗后，救援部门称他们重新控制了大部分火势 ■ 以下是战争开始 242 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-242-hezbollah-says-it-does-not-want-to-expand-conflict/0000018f-e417-d1da-adaf-f59f16220001</guid></item><item><title>世界中央厨房处于“高度戒备”状态，全面恢复在加沙的人道主义行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/on-very-high-alert-world-central-kitchen-fully-resumes-humanitarian-operations-in-gaza/0000018f-e3b6-d6de-a7df-f7be1dc00000</link><description>世界中央厨房在加沙设有 68 个正常运转的社区厨房，自以色列空袭导致 7 名志愿者死亡两个月后恢复活动以来，该厨房已提供了超过 350 万份餐食</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 15:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/on-very-high-alert-world-central-kitchen-fully-resumes-humanitarian-operations-in-gaza/0000018f-e3b6-d6de-a7df-f7be1dc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将不会参加下一届威尼斯建筑双年展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-take-part-in-the-next-venice-architecture-biennale/0000018f-e2b6-d5cf-adcf-ffbe0cff0000</link><description>据以色列官员透露，以色列因展馆翻修，将不会在2025年举办展览。但正如一位艺术官员在加沙战争的背景下所说的那样，“现在当我们被排斥时，正是我们参与其中的时候”</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 15:23:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-take-part-in-the-next-venice-architecture-biennale/0000018f-e2b6-d5cf-adcf-ffbe0cff0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的破坏、饥饿和死亡是以色列的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/the-destruction-starvation-and-death-in-gaza-are-israels-defeat/0000018f-e31a-dce5-abdf-e33f1d9a0000</link><description>犹太国家之所以被击败