.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/firefighters-continue-to-battle-blazes-in-north-israel-thousands-of-acres-already-burned/0000018f-e26a-da42-a1ef-fafa7c140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战火，以色列人垂死挣扎，而内塔尼亚胡在国会为阿谀奉承者精心准备演讲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-in-flames-israelis-are-dying-netanyahus-only-plan-pick-a-tie-for-d-c-speech/0000018f-e299-df97-a78f-f2fb51db0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的分析人士不断将宏伟计划归功于以色列总理。但没有计划——只有一个绝望、无能的领导人，操纵着一个曾经繁荣的国家，他根本不关心人质及其家人</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-in-flames-israelis-are-dying-netanyahus-only-plan-pick-a-tie-for-d-c-speech/0000018f-e299-df97-a78f-f2fb51db0000</guid></item></channel></rss>